description:
                            KillMyConnection - 2010kaiser
                            ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~


For your convenience, I've created this little App. (Less than 5MB) for anyone who gets a little lost when told to 'Disconnect Your Internet' or 'Disable Your network Adapters' when installing 'Cracked' software.

Now it couldn't be easier. Just follow the steps below:

Instructions:
=============

To Disable Network Adapters:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

1. Right click on 'KillMyConnection-2010kaiser' and select 'Run As Administrator'.
2. Click on 'DISABLE LAC + WNC'



Your Network Adapters for 'Local Area Connection' and 'Wireless Network Connection' are now disabled.



To Re-Enable your Network Adapters:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

1. Right click on 'KillMyConnection-2010kaiser' and select 'Run As Administrator'.
2. Click on 'ENABLE LAC + WNC'.



Your Network Adapters have now been Re-Enabled.

